  - m_Id: 441432821760
    m_Localized: Deep in a remote mountain region lies Athus, an unconquered dungeon.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7361887621120
    m_Localized: Right in front of it stands a guild built to support adventurers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7454170697728
    m_Localized: (Sigh...) At this rate, how could I ever face the Guild Masters
      who came before me...?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7635096195072
    m_Localized: "(Just then, as Sherry Athus, the guild\u2019s current manager,
      lets out a deep sigh...)"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7637562445824
    m_Localized: (RUMBLE...!)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7639613460480
    m_Localized: "(A hot spring suddenly bursts forth from the guild\u2019s front
      yard!)"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7641760944128
    m_Localized: "I-it\u2019s a miracle! With this hot spring, we can bring people
      back here!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7674396823552
    m_Localized: (Sherry Athus immediately sent a proposal to headquarters to renovate
      the guild into an onsen inn.)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7676976320512
    m_Localized: "You must be the one dispatched from headquarters. I\u2019ve been
      expecting you!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7679610343424
    m_Localized: "I\u2019m Sherry Athus, the manager of this guild and a descendant
      of the Athus family. I look forward to working with you."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7681250316288
    m_Localized: "We don\u2019t have much time, so let\u2019s get started right away.
      First, let\u2019s tap the [Build] button and construct our first onsen facility."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7686904238080
    m_Localized: "Perfect! I can\u2019t believe I\u2019m seeing a real hot spring
      with my own eyes after only reading about it in reports...!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7688015728640
    m_Localized: "But we can\u2019t just leave it there on its own, can we? Please
      build a road leading to the onsen so our guests can move around comfortably."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7688955252736
    m_Localized: Great. Now the basic preparations for welcoming guests are complete.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7689882193920
    m_Localized: "And don\u2019t worry if you place a facility in the wrong spot.
      You can always move or demolish an existing facility by long-pressing it. I\u2019ll
      make sure all the paperwork is handled properly."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7690813329408
    m_Localized: Oh, and have you checked the [Upgrade] button in the facility info?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7691715104768
    m_Localized: Once the guild has gathered enough resources, you can upgrade your
      facilities.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7692713349120
    m_Localized: "The better your facilities become, the more the guild\u2019s revenue
      and reputation will grow. Let\u2019s make upgrading every facility our first
      goal."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
